<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-gold-400"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-navy-900 text-white p-10 lg:p-12">
          <p class="text-gold-300 text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6">Our Standard</p>
          <blockquote class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-snug">
            "We measure success not by the size of the matter, but by whether the client would entrust us with the next one."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
            <div class="font-medium">Satinder Hunjan KC</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-white/60">Co-Founder and Chairman</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-gold-400"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2">
      <p class="text-gold-600 text-sm tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4">About the Firm</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-navy-900 leading-tight">
        Senior attention.<br />
        <span class="italic text-gold-600">Without exception.</span>
      </h2>
      <span class="gold-divider"></span>
      <p class="text-navy-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
        ALSA Law is a senior-counsel boutique with offices in Abu Dhabi and London. Founded in 2025 by silks and senior advocates with decades of experience at the highest levels of the Bar, the firm was built on a simple promise: every client matter receives the partner-level judgment our founders spent their careers building.
      </p>
      <p class="text-navy-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        That promise shapes every hire, every practice decision, and every client relationship. We turn down more work than we accept — because the alternative would dilute the standard our clients depend on.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-lg">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-400 pl-4">
          <div class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-900">60+ Years</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">Combined Experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-400 pl-4">
          <div class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-900">40+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">Government &amp; Institutional Entities Advised</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden border-l-2 border-gold-400 pl-4">
          <div class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-900">Best Lawyers</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">42 attorneys recognized</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-400 pl-4">
          <div class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-900">2 Offices</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">Abu Dhabi · London</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
